track_notes: I caught the bus from Kitzbuhel to Kirchberg, walked over Rauher Kopf down to Reith and after a beer, caught the bus from there back to Kitzbuhel. Lovely walk with my friend Chris from Ryedale Walking Group when we were on holiday in August 2019.
track_title: Linear walk from Kirchberg to Reith via Rauher Kopf
